            <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" />Baseboards & ceiling fans</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" />Inside appliances</li>
