          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Complete cleaning for empty homes. Whether you're moving to Ardmore or relocating, we ensure the property is spotless from top to bottom.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" />Empty home deep clean</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" />All cabinets & closets</li>
